snippet.title: There Came an Echo Story Trailer
snippet.description:
Discover the pulse-pounding, sci-fi storyline inside There Came an Echo, brought to life by Wil Wheaton, Ashly Burch, Laura Bailey, Yuri Lowenthal, and others. Coming to Steam February 24th!

Soundtrack by Big Giant Circles and Ronald Jenkees! The tune in the video is the "There Came an Echo Main Theme", by BGC!
